# ── Raw photography ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1.8 GB of full-resolution exports (single files up to 24 MB). These are the
# SOURCE for assets/images/*.jpg — they are never served, and committing them
# would make the repo unusable on GitHub and stall every Vercel deploy.
#
# The delivery crops in assets/images/ (~2 MB) ARE committed. Keep this folder
# locally (or in Drive); re-run the crop pipeline when a new selection is
# needed — see assets/images/README.md.
assets/images/New folder/

# ── Build intermediates ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The build SCRIPTS are committed (build/*.mjs) and so are their OUTPUTS
# (assets/css/build.min.css, assets/js/*.min.js) — that's what makes the repo
# deployable on Vercel with zero build step. Only the throwaway middles are
# ignored.
build/vendor/
build/tw.css
build/*.bak

# ── Node ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm/
.cache/

# ── Tooling / env ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.vercel
dist/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── OS / editor ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/
